description:
Diatrix is ​​a passionate person who lives in the desert near Outland. Known as a villain to her friends, she travels through barren lands riding on her trusty hound, Argus. 

She was once a member of a gang, Diatrix committed abominations throughout her childhood, but she has since been left alone with her. Possessing her innate talent for blacksmithing, she is armed with a variety of weapons and guards her trusty plasma gun, Ol` Juggernaut. 

But aside from a few tricks and a significant retirement, her former engineer has left a lot more interesting. It was an incomplete circuit bio weapon that was long forgotten.
